{
  "chapter": 12,
  "chapter_summary": "第十二回 郭大路的拳头\n\n本章讲述了郭大路、燕七、王动、林太平四人与何雅风（实为南宫丑）的对峙。何雅风以宴请为名，实则暗藏杀机。一条黑狗突然闯入，打翻酒杯，何雅风出手抓住猫狗，却被郭大路和燕七拦下。随后狗突然死亡，众人发现酒中有毒。\n\n黑衣人（南宫丑）现身，与林太平对峙。郭大路主动请战，以拳头击败黑衣人。众人发现黑衣人剑鞘中藏有两柄剑，剑是从旁边\"挥\"出而非\"拔\"出。\n\n事后众人埋葬黑狗，感慨狗比人更讲义气。最后讨论如何处理被俘的南宫丑，决定让他自己养活自己，逼问珠宝下落。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既然如此，我们就得回去准备了。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快去，越快越好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你急什么，算你赢了就是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他什么也没；有说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎么输的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我生怕各位不肯赏光，他却说……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他说的话，我不敢说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你只管放心说，绝对没有人怪你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若是有人怪我呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也那没关系，我保护你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实他也不能算是脸皮厚，只不过是人穷志短……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "而且是饿死鬼投胎。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们到底是客人，你怎么好意思去吃人家的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁摆架子？我只不过想要他把酒菜送到这里来而已。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_ya_feng",
      "speaker_name": "何雅风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭兄在说什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我在说他……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他酒倒得太慢了，我简直已有些迫不及待。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭兄先等一等，这第一杯酒，应该我敬四位，四位一齐……",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我喜欢猫，尤其是好请客的猫。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我喜欢狗，尤其是好喝酒的狗。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜这不是金毛狮子狗。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜这不是烤鸭。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "四位说的话，小弟为何总是听不懂？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也许我们都在说醉话。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "砰",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也许这并不是黑狗，只不过穿了黑衣服。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他说他去去就来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你听见了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你相信？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "相信。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为他根本不到别地方去，他就在这帘子后换衣服。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们为什么不去换衣服？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……我没有带衣服来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这里没有衣服换，难道不会回家去换？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来这人的脸皮是厚，心倒不黑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来是你，你没有死。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只因你还不懂得杀人，也不会杀人。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我已学会了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这么样说来，阁下莫非很有杀人的天分。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_ya_feng",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还过得去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们还活着，真该谢谢那条狗。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我发现了一样事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他至少很有杀狗的天分，因为他至少杀了条狗。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也发现了一件事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他不是南宫丑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为他不丑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "名字叫南宫丑，人并不一定就会很丑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，就好像名字叫王动的人，并不一定喜欢动。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "答对了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但他脸上也没有刀疤。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁看过南宫丑脸上有刀疤？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "至少我没有看见过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他既然从不以真面目见人，谁能看到他的脸？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，也许他刀疤在屁股上。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哪样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_ya_feng",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不杀人，只杀狗。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来你也很坦白。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_ya_feng",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我刚才杀了一条，你是第二条。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "月黑风高杀人夜",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杀人",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这人倒很有耐心。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要杀人，就要有耐心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "耐心杀不了人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以我也不急。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我虽然是厚脸皮，却不是胆小鬼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对付这种人，我们本不必讲什么江湖道义。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你想四个打一个？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么不行？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是你……你有没有把握对付他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这比喻虽然狗屁不通，却说明了一件事。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有些事本就是非做不可的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，你去，他若杀了你，我替你报仇。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你放心，我不会上当的。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我真不懂，有些人为什么总是硬要充英雄。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也许他本来就是英雄——有些人天生就是英雄。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可惜英雄大多都死得早。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_ya_feng",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你的剑呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我的剑已送当铺了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你敢以空对我？是不是还怕死得不够快？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_ya_feng",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，我成全你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "砰",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也许因为我是个傻子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我根本没有看出来，我是猜出来的。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若是猜错了呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不会猜错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为我的运气好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我还有件事不懂。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他的手比剑短得多，为什么一伸手就能将剑拔出来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也不懂。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我懂。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也懂了。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "拔",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "挥",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这就好像鸡蛋一样。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "像鸡蛋？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知不知道要用什么法子才能把鸡蛋站在桌子上？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他若不来，我们就要往棺材里去了。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "狗不像人，狗不记仇，只记得住别人的恩惠。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，你只要给狗吃过一块骨头，它下次见了你，一定会摇尾巴；但有些忘恩负义的人，你无论给过他多少好处，他回过头来反而会咬你一口，所以……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以狗比人讲义气，至少比某些人讲义气。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以我们应该替它立个碑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "碑上写什么呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "义犬之墓。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "义犬两个字还不够，你莫忘记，它也是我们的救命恩人……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "碑不妨后立，祭文却不可不先读。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你会作祭文？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 540
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "棺中一狗，恩朋义友，你若不来，我们已走，初一十五，香花奠酒，呜呼哀哉……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这人将棺材送来的时候，一定已知道南宫丑并没有死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 554
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他早已知道南宫丑的阴谋。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为他不想跟我们见面。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 564,
      "line_end": 564
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我看这人一定是个女人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 570
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎见得？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 572,
      "line_end": 572
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只有女人才会做这些鬼鬼祟祟、莫名其妙的事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 574,
      "line_end": 574
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫忘记你也是男人。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 580,
      "line_end": 580
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫忘记你也是女人生出来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 582,
      "line_end": 582
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "男人天生就看不起女人，女人也天生就看不起男人，这本是天经地义的事，几千百年前如此，几千百年后一定还是这样，所以……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 584,
      "line_end": 584
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 586,
      "line_end": 586
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "多了个什么问题？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 596,
      "line_end": 596
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "南宫丑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 598,
      "line_end": 598
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，他的确是个问题。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 608,
      "line_end": 608
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他不是已经被我们关起来了吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 610,
      "line_end": 610
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 612,
      "line_end": 612
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怕他会逃走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 614,
      "line_end": 614
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他逃不了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 616,
      "line_end": 616
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既然逃不了，还有什么问题？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 620,
      "line_end": 620
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们连自己都快养不活了，怎么养得起别人？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 628,
      "line_end": 628
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们不如放了他吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 630,
      "line_end": 630
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这种人也放不得。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 632,
      "line_end": 632
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么我们难道要养他一辈子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 634,
      "line_end": 634
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以这才是问题。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 636,
      "line_end": 636
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们可以要他自己养自己。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 638,
      "line_end": 638
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，他比我们有钱得多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 640,
      "line_end": 640
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "至少他刚从风栖梧身上捞了一票。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 642,
      "line_end": 642
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你问得出？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 648,
      "line_end": 648
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我虽不是夹棍，但也有我的法子。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 650,
      "line_end": 650
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来这个人已从夹棍那里学会了几套。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 652,
      "line_end": 652
    }
  ],
